dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Waukesha County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waukesha_HydroLine_2014.gdb. [The planimetric mapping product covers the entire county and was compiled at a scale of 1' = 100'. The accuracy standard used is National Map Accuracy for 1' = 100' scale mapping. The planimetric files are non-overlapping, 2-D Microstation .dgn files and are tiled by survey township.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://data-waukeshacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/
